You must have installed Xcode.
Install macports http://www.macports.org/
ZlomekFS was build and tested under Mac OS X 10.7.
Install packages:
cmake
openssl
pkg-config
unzip
subversion
libconfig
fuse
google test

For build use ./makeall.sh script

#prepare configuration
cp -a conf/etc/zfsd /etc/
cp -a conf/var/zfs /var/
mkdir -p /var/zfs/data

#launch
./build/zfsd/zfsd/zfsd z

These is issue with fuse arguments, you must have zlomek fs local config file on /etv/zfsd/zfsd.conf.

 




